<main class="aboutt">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="about-hero">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1 class="hero-title">Our Story of Craftsmanship</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">For over three decades, Aurela Jewelry has been creating timeless pieces that celebrate life's most precious moments with exceptional quality and design.</p>
                    <a href="#story" class="hero-cta">Discover Our Journey <i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Story Section -->
        <section id="story" class="story-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Our Heritage</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">A legacy of excellence since 1990</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="story-content">
                    <div class="story-image animate-on-scroll">
                        <img src="/images/pic2.jpg" alt="Jewelry Crafting Process">
                        <div class="image-caption">Master Craftsman at Work</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="story-text">
                        <h3>From Humble Beginnings</h3>
                        <p>Founded in 1990 by master goldsmith Aurela , Aurela Jewelry began as a small boutique in Islamabad, Pakistan. With a passion for traditional craftsmanship and an eye for contemporary design, Aurela established a reputation for creating pieces that blend timeless elegance with modern sophistication.</p>
                
                        <p>Today, under the leadership of Aurela's daughter, Zujaja, we continue this legacy while embracing sustainable practices and ethical sourcing. Each piece in our collection tells a story of artistry, passion, and commitment to excellence.</p>
                        
                        <div class="milestones">
                            <div class="milestone">
                                <div class="milestone-number">1990</div>
                                <div class="milestone-text">Founded in Islamabad, Pakistan</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="milestone">
                                <div class="milestone-number">2005</div>
                                <div class="milestone-text">Expanded to International Markets</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="milestone">
                                <div class="milestone-number">2018</div>
                                <div class="milestone-text">Achieved Carbon Neutral Certification</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="milestone">
                                <div class="milestone-number">2023</div>
                                <div class="milestone-text">10,000+ Satisfied Customers Worldwide</div>
                            </div>
                            
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Values Section -->
        <section class="values-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Our Values</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">The principles that guide everything we do</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="values-grid">
                    <div class="value-card ">
                        <div class="value-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Uncompromising Quality</h3>
                        <p>We use only the finest materials and employ traditional techniques alongside modern technology to ensure every piece meets our exacting standards.</p>
                        <ul class="value-list">
                            <li>100% genuine materials</li>
                            <li>Hand-inspected by experts</li>
                            <li>Lifetime craftsmanship warranty</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="value-card ">
                        <div class="value-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Ethical Integrity</h3>
                        <p>Transparency, fair practices, and responsible sourcing are at the heart of everything we do, from mine to market.</p>
                        <ul class="value-list">
                            <li>Conflict-free diamonds</li>
                            <li>Fair trade gold & silver</li>
                            <li>Ethical labor practices</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="value-card ">
                        <div class="value-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Customer Commitment</h3>
                        <p>We build lasting relationships with our clients, providing personalized service and standing behind every piece with our lifetime warranty.</p>
                        <ul class="value-list">
                            <li>Personalized consultations</li>
                            <li>Free resizing for 1 year</li>
                            <li>24/7 customer support</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="value-card ">
    <div class="value-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
    </div>
    <h3>Sustainable Future</h3>
    <p>We're committed to reducing our environmental impact and contributing to a more sustainable jewelry industry.</p>
    <ul class="value-list">
        <li>Carbon neutral operations</li>
        <li>Recycled packaging</li>
        <li>Solar-powered workshops</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="value-card ">
    <div class="value-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-female"></i>
    </div>
    <h3>Women Empowerment</h3>
    <p>Founded and led by women, we actively train and employ female artisans across Pakistan, creating opportunities and economic independence.</p>
    <ul class="value-list">
        <li>85% female workforce</li>
        <li>Skill development programs</li>
        <li>Leadership training for women</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="value-card ">
    <div class="value-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
    </div>
    <h3>Artisan Partnership</h3>
    <p>We work directly with master artisans, ensuring fair wages and preserving Pakistan's traditional jewelry-making heritage.</p>
    <ul class="value-list">
        <li>Fair trade partnerships</li>
        <li>Traditional technique preservation</li>
        <li>Direct artisan payments</li>
    </ul>
</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Craftsmanship Section -->
        <section class="craftsmanship-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
