                </div>
                
                <div class="craftsmanship-content">
                    <div class="craftsmanship-text">
                        <h3>Meticulous Attention to Detail</h3>
                        <p>Our design philosophy is simple: create pieces that will be cherished for generations. Each collection begins with inspiration from nature, architecture, and cultural motifs from around the world.</p>
                        <p>Our team of designers works closely with master craftspeople to transform these inspirations into wearable art. From initial sketch to final polish, every step is executed with precision and care, resulting in jewelry that's as meaningful as it is beautiful.</p>
                        
                        <div class process-steps">
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <h4>Design & Inspiration</h4>
                                    <p>Each piece begins as a hand-drawn sketch, inspired by timeless beauty and modern aesthetics.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <h4>Material Selection</h4>
                                    <p>We carefully select only the highest quality metals and gemstones from ethical sources.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="process-step">
                                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <h4>Hand Crafting</h4>
                                    <p>Master artisans shape, set, and polish each piece with traditional techniques perfected over decades.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="craftsmanship-image ">
                        <img src="/images/pic1.jpg" alt="Jewelry Design Process">
                        <div class="image-caption">Design Studio - Where Ideas Become Reality</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

